quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  109,4,"Èmi kò níí jọ́sìn fún ohun tí ẹ jọ́sìn fún sẹ́."
  109,5,"Ẹ̀yin náà kò kú jọ́sìn fún Ẹni tí mò ń jọ́sìn fún."
  109,6,"Tiyín ni ẹ̀sìn yín, tèmi sì ni ẹ̀sìn mi.”"
  110,1,"Nígbà tí àrànṣe Allāhu (lórí ọ̀tá ẹ̀sìn) àti ṣíṣí ìlú (Mọ́kkah) bá ṣẹlẹ̀,"
  110,2,"tí o sì rí àwọn ènìyàn tí wọ́n wọnú ẹ̀sìn Allāhu níjọníjọ,"
  110,3,"nítorí náà, ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ àti ẹyìn fún Olúwa rẹ. Kí o sì tọrọ àforíjìn lọ́dọ̀ Rẹ̀.Dájúdájú Ó ń jẹ́ Olùgba-ìronúpìwàdà. {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Gọ̄fir;  40:55.]
